@552 = ~Letter to Sibel~
@553 = ~Dear Sibel,

Your father was not a sincere man. Did he tell you that you are a member of Amberville family? Your mother was an Amberville - a fact most certainly hidden from you by your sire. The amulet inside the envelope is my proof. Only a member of Amberville family could wear it. Try it on. The amulet would resist you, were you not an Amberville.

Pay heed to my words, child! The path ahead of you is wrought with peril. Arcanis family has already been defeated, yet Virtus Arcanis lives still. I fear he may approach you soon, deceit on his mind. Remain vigilant and do not fall prey to his schemes. Make a wise decision and stand with your mother's family.

Your great ancestor,
Lawrence Amberville~
@554 = ~Necklace of the Rich~
@555 = ~Judgement Day +5~
@556 = ~Judgement Day +5

Far long ago, a party of Barbarians and mages attacked a compound of powerful evil enemies led by a Demon Prince who had many minions including powerful demons and golems. The good party was well prepared for such a great combat, but the number of enemies were way more than they had thought. They killed many of the evil foes, but eventually all of them fell in that unfair battle. When the last of them was dying of numerous fatal wounds, he wished with his last breath that their souls remain as an essence in the universe to make a mighty weapon for a judgement day when the good are to meet the evil in their greatest battle.

This is the outstanding weapon after being finally forged.

Equipped abilities:
Immunity to Fear, Charm, Confusion and Backstab.
+2 Bonus to Strength
+30 Max hit points while equipped
+20% Resistance to Crushing, Slashing, piercing and missile damage.

Special abilities:
With each successful hit:
10% chance to heal the wielder for 40 points.
30% chance to trigger a random beneficial mage spell. The total 30% probability is distributed as follows:

Blur: 2%
Mirror Image: 4%
Stoneskin: 4%
Oracle: 3%
Lower Resistance (on target): 4%
Improved Haste: 2%
Protection from Magical Weapons: 4%
Globe of invulnerability: 3%
Spell turning: 2%
Protection from Energy: 2%

THAC0: +5 bonus
Damage: 2D8 + 5
Damage type: slashing
Weight: 2
Speed Factor: 0
Proficiency Type: Long Sword
Type: 1-handed
Requires: 17 Strength
Usable By:
 Good aligned single-class fighters and paladins~
